description: The Journey Series of men's wovens feature a casual collar styling, made from an Organic Cotton/Linen blend. Translating to “bird” from te reo Tahiti, a certain nimble and vibrant manu sung us through trails while trekking through the lush island interior. The Manu Floral celebrates this creature’s song.
name: Roark Journey Manu Floral Woven SS - Mens
